erbetle&#351;megi g&uuml;&yacute;zde we &yacute;azda &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;yk&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Keseli&#328; diagnozy</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Kliniki barlag</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Lukman garyn du&yacute;gusy
bilen umumy &yacute;agda&yacute;a baha ber&yacute;&auml;r, a&#351;gazan
&yacute;erind&auml;ki agyryny kesgitle&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Ganazlygy&#328;
alamatlaryna &uuml;ns berip biler: derini&#328; re&#328;klenmegi,
sa&ccedil;lary&#328; we dyrnaklary&#328; pesligi, pes gan basy&#351;y.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Laboratori&yacute;a usullary</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Olar k&ouml;mek&ccedil;i
h&auml;si&yacute;ete e&yacute;e.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Gany&#328; kliniki der&#328;ewind&auml;ki&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&uuml;&yacute;tge&#351;meler&nbsp;a&yacute;ratyn
d&auml;l.&nbsp;Gemoglobini&#328; we eritrositleri&#328; derejesini&#328;
peselmegi bilen gizlin gan akma &#351;&uuml;bhelenmeli.&nbsp;Le&yacute;kositoz
we k&ouml;pel&yacute;&auml;n ESR a&#351;gazan &yacute;arasyny&#328;
&ccedil;yl&#351;yrymly g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;lerinde &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;yk&yacute;ar (mysal &uuml;&ccedil;in, &yacute;arany&#328;
arala&#351;magy).&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>I&ccedil;ki gan akma g&uuml;man edil&yacute;&auml;n&nbsp;<b>fekal
okkult gan barlagy&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>H. pylori antigen &uuml;&ccedil;in&nbsp;<b>dem aly&#351; karbamid
synagy&nbsp;</b>&yacute;a-da&nbsp;<b>tabul&nbsp;synagy&nbsp;</b>,
i&#351;je&#328; H. pylori &yacute;okan&ccedil;lygyny &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;ykarmak &uuml;&ccedil;in &yacute;&ouml;neke&yacute; we hassalar
&uuml;&ccedil;in amatly usuldyr.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Instrumental g&ouml;zleg</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Esasy anykla&yacute;y&#351; usuly&nbsp;<b>&ouml;zofagogastroduodenoskopi&yacute;a
(EGDS)&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;Bu endoskopiki usul, &yacute;arany tapmaga, kem&ccedil;iligi&#328;
takyk &yacute;erini, ululygyny, &ccedil;u&#328;lugyny kesgitlem&auml;ge
m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik ber&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Cerarany&#328;
gyralaryny&#328; we d&uuml;&yacute;b&uuml;ni&#328; &yacute;agda&yacute;yna
g&ouml;r&auml;, &yacute;arany&#328; fazasy kesgitlen&yacute;&auml;r -
g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;lenmek &yacute;a-da &ouml;tmek.&nbsp;K&auml;bir
hadysalarda mikroskopiki g&ouml;zden ge&ccedil;irmek &uuml;&ccedil;in sagdyn
dokumany&#328; we &yacute;arany&#328; serhedind&auml;ki bir &yacute;eri&#328;
biopsi&yacute;asy edil&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Se&yacute;rek &yacute;agda&yacute;larda, EGDS
kontrendikasi&yacute;a edilende,&nbsp;<b>rentgen barlagy&nbsp;</b>ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;.&nbsp;G&ouml;ni
g&ouml;ni onu&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;nde n&auml;sag &yacute;&ouml;rite
kontrast seri&#351;desini i&ccedil;&yacute;&auml;r, so&#328;ra bir topar
g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik suratlary alyn&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Munu&#328; tersine, a&#351;gazany&#328;
we on iki barmakly i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; diwarlaryny&#328;
&yacute;e&#328;ille&#351;megi a&yacute;dy&#328; g&ouml;r&uuml;n&yacute;&auml;r
- &yacute;arany&#328; barlygynda, kontrast seri&#351;desi
&yacute;ygnan&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Intragastriki pH-e g&uuml;ndelik g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>- on
iki barmakly i&ccedil;ege &yacute;aralary bilen k&ouml;plen&ccedil;
a&#351;gazan &yacute;aralary bilen kislotany&#328; k&ouml;pelmegi - adaty
&yacute;a-da pesel&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi maksatlary</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergini&#328; maksady,
&yacute;arany&#328; seb&auml;bini &yacute;ok etmekdir.&nbsp;Adat&ccedil;a,
bejergide H. pylori bakteri&yacute;asyny &ouml;ld&uuml;rmek, eger bar bolsa
NSAID-leri &yacute;ok etmek &yacute;a-da azaltmak we &yacute;arany dermanlar bilen
bejermekde k&ouml;mek bermek &yacute;aly zatlar bar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>K&ouml;p halatlarda
ambulatori&yacute;a esasynda bejergi al&yacute;arlar.&nbsp;Gaty agyry sindromy,
kyn&ccedil;ylyklary&#328; &yacute;okary t&ouml;wekgel&ccedil;iligi bilen, has
gi&#328;i&#351;le&yacute;in g&ouml;zden ge&ccedil;irmek, agyr kesel keselleri,
hassahana &yacute;erle&#351;dirilmegi zerurdyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351; &yacute;oly we
gurallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Peptiki &yacute;arany bejermek
hemmetarapla&yacute;yn bolmalydyr.&nbsp;Di&#328;e dermanlar &yacute;eterlik
d&auml;l, durmu&#351;y&#328;yzy &uuml;&yacute;tgetmeli.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>I&yacute;mit nahary&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>- &yacute;ygy-&yacute;ygydan
fraksi&yacute;a nahary (g&uuml;nde 5-6 gezek);&nbsp;kislotany&#328;
b&ouml;l&uuml;nip &ccedil;ykmagyna itergi ber&yacute;&auml;n
&ouml;n&uuml;mlerden (g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;li et we balyk &ccedil;orbalary,
gowrulan we &yacute;akymly i&yacute;mitler, kakadylan etler we konserwirlenen
i&yacute;mitler, tagamlar we ysly zatlar (sogan, sarymsak, bur&ccedil;,
gor&ccedil;isa), duz we marinad, gazlandyrylan miwe suwlary, piwo, gury ak
&ccedil;akyr, &#351;ampan, kofe, sitrus);&nbsp;artykma&ccedil; kislotany
(ga&yacute;nadylan et we balyk, p&uuml;resi &ccedil;orbalar, d&auml;neler,
jele, jele) baglap we zy&yacute;ansyzlandyryp bil&yacute;&auml;n
&ouml;n&uuml;mlere artykma&ccedil;lyk berilmelidir;&nbsp;i&yacute;mitleri
&#351;ol bir wagty&#328; &ouml;z&uuml;nde, asuda atmosferada, &yacute;uwa&#351;-&yacute;uwa&#351;dan,
oturyp, gowy &ccedil;e&yacute;nemek gerek.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&Ccedil;ilimi&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>we&nbsp;<b>alkogoly&nbsp;</b>ta&#351;lamak&nbsp;.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Ceraralary&#328;&nbsp;<b>(NSAID) d&ouml;remegine k&ouml;mek&nbsp;</b>ed&yacute;&auml;n
dermanlary kabul etmekden &yacute;&uuml;z &ouml;w&uuml;rmek&nbsp;.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>I&#351; we dyn&ccedil; aly&#351; d&uuml;zg&uuml;nini
kadala&#351;dyrmak&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:
"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>,&nbsp;<b>&#351;ypahana bejergisi&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Dermanlar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>H. pylori &yacute;oka&#351;an
&yacute;agda&yacute;ynda&nbsp;&yacute;&ouml;rite antibakterial dermanlar we
proton nasos ingibitorlaryny&#328; kombinasi&yacute;asy arkaly&nbsp;<b>bakteri&yacute;alary
&yacute;ok etmek (&yacute;ok etmek) &uuml;&ccedil;in&nbsp;</b>&yacute;&ouml;rite
bejergi ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;.&nbsp;Bu usul, a&#351;gazan
&yacute;arasy keselini hasam g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;lendirmezden bejerm&auml;ge
m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik ber&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Proton nasos ingibitorlary (PPI)&nbsp;</span></b><span
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>-
a&#351;gazan yarasy keselini bejermek &uuml;&ccedil;in esasy dermanlar, kislotany
peseld&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Bar bolan &yacute;aralary bejermek &uuml;&ccedil;in
&#351;ertler d&ouml;red&yacute;&auml;rler we t&auml;zelerini&#328;
&ouml;smegini&#328; &ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni al&yacute;arlar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>H2 blokirle&yacute;jiler&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>a&#351;gazandaky
gidroklor tur&#351;usyny&#328; b&ouml;l&uuml;nip &ccedil;ykmagyny bas&yacute;an
dermanlardyr.&nbsp;API-leri&#328; t&auml;sirliliginden pesdirler,
&#351;onu&#328; &uuml;&ccedil;in olar bilen bilelikde &yacute;a-da bellemek
m&uuml;mkin bolmadyk mahaly alyn&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Antasidler&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>a&#351;gazany&#328; mazmunyny
zy&yacute;ansyzlandyryp, b&ouml;l&uuml;nip &ccedil;ykan kislotany
bagla&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Bu dermanlar k&ouml;plen&ccedil; agyryny a&yacute;yrmak
&uuml;&ccedil;in kabul edil&yacute;&auml;r;&nbsp;uzak wagtlap ulanmak bilen,
PPI we H2-blokatorlardan tapawutlylykda, zy&yacute;anly t&auml;sirleri bolup
biler (i&ccedil; gatamagy, i&ccedil;ge&ccedil;me we &#351;.m.).&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Be&yacute;leki dermanlar&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>a&#351;gazany&#328; we
on iki barmakly i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; gyjyndyrmasynda gora&yacute;jy gatlak
d&ouml;red&yacute;&auml;n sitoprotektiki seri&#351;deler
di&yacute;il&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergini&#328; netijeliligine
baha bermek we &yacute;arany&#328; &uuml;&yacute;tgemegine
g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik etmek &uuml;&ccedil;in endoskopiki barlag (EGDS)
ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Cerarany&#328; howply kyn&ccedil;ylyklary &yacute;a-da olary&#328;
d&ouml;remek howpy bar bolsa, operasi&yacute;a edilmelidir.&nbsp;Bu
&yacute;agda&yacute;larda zeper &yacute;eten organy&#328; bir b&ouml;legini
g&ouml;zden ge&ccedil;irmek (mysal &uuml;&ccedil;in, b&ouml;lekle&yacute;in
gastrektomi&yacute;a - zeper &yacute;eten a&#351;gazany&#328; bir b&ouml;legini
a&yacute;yrmak) &yacute;a-da diwardaky kem&ccedil;ilik tikil&yacute;&auml;r
(organlary gora&yacute;an operasi&yacute;a).</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Derman bejergisini&#328; t&auml;siri &yacute;ok bolsa,
operasi&yacute;a k&ouml;mek edip biler.&nbsp;Operasi&yacute;a usullary
a&#351;gazany&#328; sekretor i&#351;ini azald&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Munu&#328;
&uuml;&ccedil;in a&#351;gazandaky nerwleri&#328; k&auml;birini
